          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The +<text styleclass="Interface2">X–axis</text> is from the <text styleclass="Interface">start-Point</text> to the <text styleclass="Interface">end-Point</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Line / CAD-Line</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Interface2">+Y-axis</text> is at <text styleclass="Interface2">+90º</text> from the <text styleclass="Interface2">+X-axis,</text> and on the <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Plane.</text></para>
